# Weather Forecast App

## Description
A simple Android application that displays real-time weather information using the OpenWeatherMap API.

## Features
- Search weather by city
- Current temperature
- Weather condition
- Humidity
- Wind speed
- Feels like temperature
- Weather icon
- Beautiful Material UI

## Technologies Used
- Java
- Android Studio
- Volley
- OpenWeatherMap API
- CardView
- Glide

